{
  "texts": [
    "There are several dimensions to this phenomenon:",
    "On the supply side, the accessibility of powerful text generators has grown.",
    "The global market for AI text generation tools was estimated at $423.8 million in 2022 and is projected to reach $2.2 billion by 2032, expanding at a rapid rate as businesses and individuals adopt these models for various uses (Dergipark, 2024).",
    "This growth means the tools are widely available and becoming cheaper, lowering the barrier for malicious use.",
    "North America currently leads in usage share, but Asia-Pacific is expected to see the fastest growth, indicating a geographically widening usage (Grand View Research, 2024)."
  ]
}